version 0.10, 21/2/2020
=======================
  o accept PUT and DEL queries

version 0.9, 14/05/2018
=======================
  o refresh code for newer OCaml compilers
  o make it possible to read the request body and set the response code
  o can set/get cookies
  o improve build (now uses ocamlfind to (un)install)
  o minor fixes

version 0.8, 24/5/2006
======================
  o no failure anymore when QUERY_STRING is not set (patch by Till Varoquaux)

